# tdd

Full workflow: `.claude/skills/tdd/SKILL.md`.

Red-green-refactor, test-first, for anything in the five backend engines. Use concrete golden-value test cases traceable to a real source (published card T&C or `docs/research/`) — not invented numbers. Add boundary tests for every milestone/cap. Never mock the reward calculation itself to make a test pass. Lighter touch (contract-level tests, not exact-wording tests) for the AI Reasoning Layer and frontend.
